14:28 Igihesha umwami icyubahiro ni uko aba afite abantu benshi cyane, Ariko iyo ababuze aba arimbutse.
14:29 Utihutira kurakara aba afite ubwenge bwinshi, Ariko uwihutira kurakara akuza ubupfu.
14:30 Umutima utuje ni wo bugingo bw'umubiri, Ariko ishyari ni nk'ikimungu kiri mu magufwa.
14:31 Urenganya umukene aba atuka Iyamuremye, Ariko ubabariye umutindi aba ayubashye.
14:32 Umunyabyaha anyitswa n'ibibi bye akora, Ariko umukiranutsi afite ubuhungiro ndetse no mu rupfu rwe.
14:33 Ubwenge buba mu mutima w'ujijutse, Ariko ibiri mu mutima w'umupfapfa biramenyekana.
14:34 Gukiranuka gushyira ubwoko hejuru, Ariko ibyaha bikoza isoni amoko yose.
