19:8 Uwishakira ubwenge aba akunda ubugingo bwe, Ukomeza kwitonda azabona ibyiza.
19:9 Umugabo w'indarikwa ntazabura guhanwa, Kandi uvuga ibinyoma azapfa abizize.
19:10 Umupfapfa ntakwiriye ibinezeza, N'umugaragu ntakwiriye gutegeka ibikomangoma.
