21:6 Ubutunzi bushakishwa ururimi rubeshya buyoka nk'umwuka, Ababushaka baba bashaka urupfu.
21:7 Urugomo rw'abanyabyaha ruzabahitana, Kuko banga gukora ibitunganye.
21:8 Inzira y'uremerewe n'ibyaha iragoramanga cyane, Ariko imirimo y'uboneye ihora itunganye.
21:9 Kuba mu gakinga k'urusenge, Biruta kubana n'umugore w'ingare mu nzu y'inyumba.
21:10 Umutima w'umunyabyaha wifuza ibyaha, Umuturanyi we ntabwo yabona ineza imuturukaho.
