21:12 Umukiranutsi yitegereza inzu y'abanyabyaha, Uko bubikwa bakarimbuka.
21:13 Uwica amatwi ngo atumva gutaka k'umukene, Na we azataka kandi ntazumvwa.
21:14 Ituro ritanzwe rwihishwa rihosha uburakari, N'impongano zihishwe mu kwaha zoroshya umujinya ukaze.
