31:4 “Ntibikwiriye abami, Lemuweli we,
31:5 Be kunywa bakibagirwa ibyategetswe,
31:6 Ibisindisha ubihe ugiye gupfa,
31:7 Mureke anywe urwo rushungandushyi,
31:8 “Bumbura akanwa kawe uvugire ikiragi,
31:9 Bumbura akanwa kawe uce imanza zitabera,
31:10 Umugore w'imico myiza ni nde wamubona?
31:11 Umutima w'umugabo we uhora umwiringira,
31:12 Ahora amugirira neza ntabwo amugirira nabi,
31:13 Ashaka ubwoya bw'intama n'imigwegwe,
31:14 Ameze nk'inkuge z'abagenza,
31:15 Abyuka kare butaracya,
31:16 Yitegereza umurima akawugura,
31:17 Akenyerana imbaraga,
31:18 Abona yuko ibyo akora bimufitiye akamaro,
31:19 Afatisha ukuboko urubambo ruriho ipamba,
31:20 Aramburira abakene ibiganza,
31:21 Ntatinyisha abo mu rugo igihe cy'imbeho,
31:22 Yibohera ibirago by'ibisuna,
31:23 Umugabo we amenyekana mu marembo y'umudugudu,
31:24 Aboha imyambaro akayigura,
31:25 Imbaraga n'icyubahiro ni byo myambaro ye,
31:26 Abumbuza akanwa ke ubwenge,
31:27 Amenya neza imico yo mu rugo rwe,
31:28 Abana be barahaguruka bakamwita Munyamugisha,
31:29 “Abagore benshi bagenza neza,
31:30 Ubutoni burashukana kandi uburanga bwiza ni ubusa,
31:31 Mumuhe ku mbuto ziva mu maboko ye,
